short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: AI CV Pro is a Chrome extension that creates a resume from your LinkedIn profile and extracts job descriptions from job posts.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Transform your LinkedIn profile into a professional resume in just a few clicks with AI CV Pro! This powerful Chrome extension leverages advanced AI technology to parse your LinkedIn data and create a polished, customizable resume tailored to showcase your skills and experience.
